1
00:00:09,038 --> 00:00:09,663
<i>C'mon!</i>

2
00:00:16,245 --> 00:00:18,805
<i>Running like a fugitive,</i>

3
00:00:19,949 --> 00:00:22,008
<i>Being chased by something</i>

4
00:00:23,686 --> 00:00:26,348
<i>Inside my heart is pounding</i>

5
00:00:27,690 --> 00:00:30,318
<i>My throat dry like it's withering</i>

6
00:00:31,961 --> 00:00:35,055
<i>For no single one,</i>

7
00:00:35,731 --> 00:00:38,791
<i>To none does belong,</i>

8
00:00:40,136 --> 00:00:44,402
<i>This time is ours, right now...</i>

9
00:00:47,176 --> 00:00:49,041
<i>Unraveling the pain,</i>

10
00:00:49,145 --> 00:00:50,874
<i>Unraveling our hearts,</i>

11
00:00:50,947 --> 00:00:53,279
<i>Unraveling shadows</i>

12
00:00:54,817 --> 00:00:56,580
<i>Stifling our breath,</i>

13
00:00:56,652 --> 00:00:58,552
<i>Reaching for beyond,</i>

14
00:00:58,621 --> 00:01:01,055
<i>Tearing through the dark</i>

15
00:01:02,959 --> 00:01:09,523
<i>In fighting and in love</i>

16
00:01:10,499 --> 00:01:13,127
<i>To the distant light above,</i>

17
00:01:13,803 --> 00:01:16,772
<i>Yes, we are on the way</i>

18
00:01:21,510 --> 00:01:22,807
<i>I wanna rock...</i>

19
00:01:25,381 --> 00:01:26,905
<i>Rockin' my heart</i>

20
00:01:38,129 --> 00:01:39,619
<i>Sasuke here at Point B!</i>

21
00:01:40,231 --> 00:01:41,858
<i>Sakura here at Point C!</i>

22
00:01:44,803 --> 00:01:46,794
<i>Naruto here. I'm at Point A!</i>

23
00:01:47,472 --> 00:01:48,439
<i>You're slow, Naruto!</i>

24
00:01:49,541 --> 00:01:51,168
<i>Okay, the seventh squad...</i>

25
00:01:51,843 --> 00:01:52,241
<i>Hm?!</i>

26
00:01:53,645 --> 00:01:54,509
<i>The target has moved!</i>

27
00:01:55,780 --> 00:01:56,269
<i>Follow it!</i>

28
00:02:03,088 --> 00:02:04,419
<i>Alright! It's over there!</i>

29
00:02:08,526 --> 00:02:09,720
What's your distance
from the target?

30
00:02:11,363 --> 00:02:14,594
Five meters!
I can go at anytime!

31
00:02:15,600 --> 00:02:16,658
I'm ready, too!

32
00:02:17,402 --> 00:02:18,198
Me, too...!

33
00:02:19,437 --> 00:02:20,062
Okay...

34
00:02:23,074 --> 00:02:23,597
Do it!

35
00:02:24,743 --> 00:02:26,142
Uryaaah!

36
00:02:27,178 --> 00:02:28,577
I got him!

37
00:02:29,414 --> 00:02:30,847
<i>Does he have the ribbon</i>
<i>on his right ear...?</i>

38
00:02:31,149 --> 00:02:32,673
<i>Are you sure it's our target Tora?</i>

39
00:02:34,285 --> 00:02:35,946
It's the target, no mistake.

40
00:02:36,755 --> 00:02:41,055
Alright, the mission to capture
lost pet "Tora" is complete!

41
00:02:42,260 --> 00:02:46,060
Isn't there a mission
with a greater sense of urgency?!

42
00:02:46,631 --> 00:02:52,570
<i>A Dangerous Mission!</i>
<i>Journey to the Land of Waves!</i>

43
00:02:54,639 --> 00:03:00,839
Ohhh! My cute Tora!
I was worried to death!

44
00:03:01,780 --> 00:03:06,217
The Wife of the Land of Fire's Daimyo (Feudal Lord)
Madame Shijimi and Tora (the Cat)

45
00:03:08,586 --> 00:03:11,111
Serves him right, that stupid cat!

46
00:03:11,589 --> 00:03:14,456
No wonder he ran away...

47
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:16,219
...Now, then!

48
00:03:16,995 --> 00:03:20,396
The next mission for
Kakashi's seventh squad is...

49
00:03:23,234 --> 00:03:28,831
An errand to the neighboring town...
to baby-sit the chief Councilor's boy...

50
00:03:29,307 --> 00:03:30,740
Helping with digging
for potatoes, eh...

51
00:03:30,842 --> 00:03:32,002
Nooooo!

52
00:03:32,410 --> 00:03:34,275
No! No, thank you!

53
00:03:34,646 --> 00:03:35,442
As for me,

54
00:03:35,513 --> 00:03:38,243
I want to do like
a more exciting mission!

55
00:03:38,550 --> 00:03:39,642
Give us something else!

56
00:03:40,051 --> 00:03:40,983
<i>He's got a point...</i>

57
00:03:41,553 --> 00:03:43,214
<i>Man... He's a pain!</i>

58
00:03:46,057 --> 00:03:48,617
<i>I thought it was about time</i>
<i>for him to get fretful...</i>

59
00:03:49,394 --> 00:03:53,330
You fool!
You're still bottom rookie!

60
00:03:53,598 --> 00:03:54,860
At the start,

61
00:03:55,066 --> 00:03:56,124
everyone moves up
the ladder

62
00:03:56,201 --> 00:03:57,998
by gaining experience
from simple missions!

63
00:03:58,069 --> 00:03:59,661
B-But!

64
00:03:59,871 --> 00:04:02,362
It's been nothing
but blah missions so far!

65
00:04:04,075 --> 00:04:05,565
Knock it off!

66
00:04:06,411 --> 00:04:07,378
Naruto!

67
00:04:08,480 --> 00:04:13,076
It's necessary to explain to you
what a mission is...

68
00:04:14,652 --> 00:04:15,414
Listen to me!

69
00:04:16,087 --> 00:04:19,614
Requests pour into the village
every day.

70
00:04:20,592 --> 00:04:23,117
They range from babysitting
to assassinations...

71
00:04:24,696 --> 00:04:28,894
A wide spectrum of requests are
recorded on the request list...

72
00:04:29,234 --> 00:04:34,831
They are separated into A, B, C,
and D ranks in order of difficulty.

73
00:04:35,640 --> 00:04:37,904
In the village,
everyone below me

74
00:04:38,042 --> 00:04:43,639
is divided up by ability in the order of
Jonin, Chunin, and Genin.

75
00:04:45,016 --> 00:04:48,349
We at the highest level distribute
the requests as missions

76
00:04:48,419 --> 00:04:51,718
to Ninjas who have abilities
that suit said mission.

77
00:04:52,357 --> 00:04:59,160
And, if the mission is successful,
the fee comes in from the client.

78
00:05:00,064 --> 00:05:04,467
Nevertheless, you guys
have just become Genin...

79
00:05:05,236 --> 00:05:07,534
rank D is about
the best you can do...

80
00:05:08,673 --> 00:05:09,196
Hm?!

81
00:05:09,674 --> 00:05:12,108
Yesterday's lunch was pork bone
broth noodles,

82
00:05:12,176 --> 00:05:13,438
so today will be miso broth...

83
00:05:13,511 --> 00:05:14,876
Listen!

84
00:05:15,346 --> 00:05:16,836
I-I'm sorry.

85
00:05:17,248 --> 00:05:21,378
Maaaan!
You always lecture me, old man!

86
00:05:21,953 --> 00:05:27,482
But I'm not that little prankster
that you think I am!

87
00:05:28,526 --> 00:05:28,958
Humph!

88
00:05:33,765 --> 00:05:35,790
<i>Maaan, I'm going to get scolded later...</i>

89
00:05:43,508 --> 00:05:47,239
<i>This kid who could only</i>
<i>express himself with pranks...</i>

90
00:05:49,514 --> 00:05:50,913
Okay, fine!

91
00:05:51,282 --> 00:05:51,611
Huh?!

92
00:05:52,283 --> 00:05:54,376
If you insist...

93
00:05:55,053 --> 00:05:57,351
I'll have you do a Rank C mission...

94
00:05:58,389 --> 00:06:00,414
You'll be bodyguards for someone.

95
00:06:00,959 --> 00:06:01,687
Really?!

96
00:06:02,493 --> 00:06:02,891
Ah ha!

97
00:06:03,294 --> 00:06:04,318
Who? Who?

98
00:06:04,862 --> 00:06:05,851
A feudal lord?!

99
00:06:06,064 --> 00:06:07,554
Or, a princess?!

100
00:06:08,032 --> 00:06:09,499
Don't get so hasty.

101
00:06:10,134 --> 00:06:11,499
I'll introduce you now!

102
00:06:13,037 --> 00:06:15,437
Could you please come in...?

103
00:06:16,574 --> 00:06:17,040
Huh?!

104
00:06:24,882 --> 00:06:29,114
What's this? It's just a bunch
of damned squirts!

105
00:06:33,591 --> 00:06:34,387
Huh?

106
00:06:39,631 --> 00:06:42,361
Particularly you, the smallest one
with the idiot face.

107
00:06:42,767 --> 00:06:45,736
Are you really a Ninja?

108
00:06:47,405 --> 00:06:50,033
Who's the smallest one with
the idiot face he's talking about?

109
00:06:50,375 --> 00:06:51,034
What?!

110
00:06:55,079 --> 00:06:56,376
I'll kill him!!

111
00:06:56,447 --> 00:06:57,880
What good will it do to
kill the old man

112
00:06:57,949 --> 00:06:59,746
you're supposed to be
guarding, you moron?!

113
00:07:03,521 --> 00:07:07,981
I'm Tazuna,
veteran bridge builder.

114
00:07:08,726 --> 00:07:12,992
You'll be risking life and limb
in guarding me to the max

115
00:07:13,464 --> 00:07:16,160
until I return to my land and
complete my bridge!

116
00:07:34,385 --> 00:07:35,852
All right!

117
00:07:36,320 --> 00:07:37,787
We're off!!

118
00:07:38,122 --> 00:07:40,454
What're you so excited about?!

119
00:07:40,992 --> 00:07:45,622
You see, I've never left
the village before!

120
00:07:45,797 --> 00:07:49,824
Hey! A m I really okay with this squirt?!

121
00:07:51,402 --> 00:07:54,667
I'm a Jonin. I'll be watching him.
There's no need to worry.

122
00:07:54,872 --> 00:07:58,273
<i>...okay with this squirt?!</i>

123
00:07:59,043 --> 00:08:01,443
<i>Anyone but this old dude, man...</i>

124
00:08:01,512 --> 00:08:02,877
<i>He's really the worst client!</i>

125
00:08:03,181 --> 00:08:04,739
<i>I'll tell him a thing or two...</i>

126
00:08:05,683 --> 00:08:06,877
Hey, old man!

127
00:08:06,951 --> 00:08:09,044
Don't be mocking Ninjas
so much!

128
00:08:09,153 --> 00:08:10,882
I'm awesome, you see!

129
00:08:11,222 --> 00:08:14,419
I'm a super elite Ninja who
will be called Hokage one day!

130
00:08:14,859 --> 00:08:17,225
My name's Naruto Uzumaki.

131
00:08:17,695 --> 00:08:18,787
Remember it well!!

132
00:08:24,335 --> 00:08:28,431
The Hokage's the super top-dog
Ninja in the village, right?

133
00:08:29,173 --> 00:08:32,267
You sure as heck don't seem like
you could become the Hokage...

134
00:08:32,944 --> 00:08:34,741
Aaah! Shut up!

135
00:08:34,946 --> 00:08:38,905
I'm prepared to do whatever
it takes to become the Hokage!

136
00:08:39,217 --> 00:08:43,677
You'll have no choice
but to acknowledge me then!!

137
00:08:45,289 --> 00:08:47,814
I'll never acknowledge you, squirt...

138
00:08:48,326 --> 00:08:50,487
Even if you become the Hokage!

139
00:08:50,661 --> 00:08:52,993
What?! I'll kill you!

140
00:08:53,231 --> 00:08:55,199
I told you to stop it, you moron!

141
00:08:55,266 --> 00:08:58,030
No! At least let me have
one shot, just one...

142
00:09:05,743 --> 00:09:07,677
Say... Mr. Tazuna...?

143
00:09:08,279 --> 00:09:09,211
What is it?

144
00:09:09,981 --> 00:09:12,779
Your country is
"The Land of the Waves," right?

145
00:09:13,785 --> 00:09:15,218
What of it?

146
00:09:15,653 --> 00:09:17,211
Say, Kakashi Sensei...

147
00:09:17,522 --> 00:09:19,217
Are there Ninjas in that land, too?

148
00:09:19,791 --> 00:09:22,555
No, there aren't Ninjas in
the Land of the Waves...

149
00:09:23,261 --> 00:09:27,960
But in other nations, while cultures
and customs are different,

150
00:09:28,533 --> 00:09:31,161
hidden villages exist,
and there are Ninjas there.

151
00:09:35,072 --> 00:09:37,472
To the many nations on the continent,

152
00:09:38,109 --> 00:09:41,875
the existence of Shinobi Villages is
a measure of the nation's military strength.

153
00:09:42,980 --> 00:09:43,912
In other words,

154
00:09:44,115 --> 00:09:47,812
that is how these nations malntain
their relationships with neighboring nations.

155
00:09:49,220 --> 00:09:53,316
Even so, the villages are not
under the control of the nations.

156
00:09:53,724 --> 00:09:55,954
They are equal in rank.

157
00:09:57,695 --> 00:10:00,186
On a small island like
the Land of the Waves,

158
00:10:00,264 --> 00:10:02,164
where it is difficult to be
influenced by other nations,

159
00:10:02,600 --> 00:10:04,898
there is no need
for a Shinobi village.

160
00:10:08,372 --> 00:10:11,170
Among the respective nations
that possess a Shinobi Village,

161
00:10:11,409 --> 00:10:17,678
the five nations of "Fire," "Water,"
"Lightning," "Wind," and "Earth,"

162
00:10:18,382 --> 00:10:21,044
due to their large territory and
immeasurable power,

163
00:10:21,319 --> 00:10:22,980
are called the "Five Great Nations."

164
00:10:25,556 --> 00:10:27,547
The Village Hidden in the Leaves
of the Land of Fire,

165
00:10:28,559 --> 00:10:30,652
the Village Hidden in the Mist
of the Land of Water,

166
00:10:31,329 --> 00:10:33,524
the Village Hidden in the Clouds
of the Land of Lightning,

167
00:10:34,198 --> 00:10:36,325
the Village Hidden in the Sand
of the Land of Wind,

168
00:10:37,335 --> 00:10:39,633
the Village Hidden in the Rocks
of the Land of Earth.

169
00:10:40,471 --> 00:10:42,530
Only the leaders of
each of these Hidden Villages

170
00:10:42,607 --> 00:10:44,871
are allowed to have
the name of Kage, the Shadow.

171
00:10:46,911 --> 00:10:48,378
The "Hokage"
(Fire shadow),"

172
00:10:48,446 --> 00:10:49,640
"Mizukage"
(Water Shadow),

173
00:10:49,714 --> 00:10:50,772
"Raikage"
(Lightning Shadow),

174
00:10:50,848 --> 00:10:51,940
"Kazekage"
(Wind Shadow),

175
00:10:52,116 --> 00:10:53,174
"Tsuchikage"
(Earth Shadow),

176
00:10:53,251 --> 00:10:55,048
the so-called
Five Kage (shadows),

177
00:10:55,119 --> 00:10:58,555
reign supreme over
the tens of thousands of Ninjas

178
00:10:58,623 --> 00:11:00,215
in each nation
of the whole world.

179
00:11:00,691 --> 00:11:03,717
No kidding...
Lord Hokage is that incredible!

180
00:11:05,129 --> 00:11:08,121
I wonder if that blah old man
is really that incredible...

181
00:11:08,399 --> 00:11:09,957
Sounds fishy!

182
00:11:14,372 --> 00:11:16,772
<i>That can't be true! No way!</i>

183
00:11:17,174 --> 00:11:17,697
Hey!

184
00:11:20,411 --> 00:11:23,403
You guys just doubted
Lord Hokage now, didn't you...?

185
00:11:28,019 --> 00:11:29,953
Well... don't worry.

186
00:11:30,821 --> 00:11:34,313
There are no Ninja battles
in Rank C missions.

187
00:11:35,026 --> 00:11:39,122
Then, there's no worry of getting
into a scrape with foreign Ninjas...!

188
00:11:39,497 --> 00:11:40,122
Of course, not.

189
00:12:33,584 --> 00:12:34,209
What?!

190
00:12:34,518 --> 00:12:34,984
Huh?!

191
00:12:35,052 --> 00:12:36,451
W-What?

192
00:12:36,921 --> 00:12:37,945
The first one!

193
00:12:48,899 --> 00:12:51,026
K- Kakashi Sensei!

194
00:12:53,671 --> 00:12:55,070
The second one...

195
00:12:58,126 --> 00:12:59,058
The second one...

196
00:13:06,634 --> 00:13:07,566
Ohhh...!

197
00:13:16,010 --> 00:13:16,476
Hm?!

198
00:13:21,683 --> 00:13:22,672
<i>It doesn't come off!</i>

199
00:13:31,226 --> 00:13:31,920
<i>W...Wow!!</i>

200
00:13:39,334 --> 00:13:39,925
Whoa!

201
00:13:40,435 --> 00:13:40,833
Ugh!!

202
00:13:41,302 --> 00:13:42,166
<i>They'll come!</i>

203
00:13:42,737 --> 00:13:44,671
<i>I have to do it...</i>
<i>I have to!!</i>

204
00:13:45,206 --> 00:13:46,434
Get back, sir!!

205
00:14:12,967 --> 00:14:13,490
Yo...

206
00:14:14,202 --> 00:14:16,898
<i>Kakashi Sensei...! He's alive!</i>

207
00:14:17,372 --> 00:14:19,169
<i>Humph!</i>
<i>Show off...</i>

208
00:14:21,776 --> 00:14:22,743
Whaa?!

209
00:14:22,810 --> 00:14:24,038
Then, what was that...?

210
00:14:26,748 --> 00:14:29,911
<i>So Kakashi Sensei...used Substitutions...</i>

211
00:14:32,921 --> 00:14:36,857
Naruto...
Sorry I didn't help you right away...

212
00:14:37,759 --> 00:14:38,817
I got you hurt.

213
00:14:40,662 --> 00:14:44,291
I didn't think you'd be
incapable of moving...

214
00:14:46,501 --> 00:14:48,628
<i>I was saved, somehow...</i>

215
00:14:52,574 --> 00:14:54,701
Anyhow, let me just say,
good job, Sasuke.

216
00:14:55,243 --> 00:14:56,175
You, too, Sakura.

217
00:14:58,580 --> 00:15:01,549
<i>I...couldn't do anything...</i>

218
00:15:02,483 --> 00:15:03,916
<i>but Sasuke...</i>

219
00:15:04,252 --> 00:15:05,947
<i>It was his first real battle...</i>

220
00:15:06,688 --> 00:15:08,952
<i>Didn't he feel scared, at all?</i>

221
00:15:09,324 --> 00:15:14,591
<i>He saved me like it was nothing and</i>
<i>without getting any dirt on his clothes...</i>

222
00:15:16,464 --> 00:15:17,055
Hey...

223
00:15:17,599 --> 00:15:18,031
Huh?!

224
00:15:18,967 --> 00:15:20,491
Are you hurt...

225
00:15:22,070 --> 00:15:23,094
scaredy cat?

226
00:15:27,375 --> 00:15:28,137
Sasuke!

227
00:15:28,242 --> 00:15:28,640
Naruto!

228
00:15:30,445 --> 00:15:32,572
These guys have poison
on their claws.

229
00:15:33,681 --> 00:15:36,343
You need to
take out the poison quickly.

230
00:15:36,551 --> 00:15:36,949
What?!

231
00:15:38,252 --> 00:15:41,346
You have to open the wound and
drain the poisoned blood.

232
00:15:41,789 --> 00:15:42,881
Don't move so much.

233
00:15:43,157 --> 00:15:44,351
The poison will spread.

234
00:15:45,526 --> 00:15:46,891
By the way, Mr. Tazuna...

235
00:15:47,061 --> 00:15:48,961
W-What is it...?!

236
00:15:50,732 --> 00:15:52,529
I have something
to talk to you about.

237
00:15:55,837 --> 00:15:58,328
Chunin from the
Village Hidden in the Mist...

238
00:15:59,140 --> 00:16:01,540
These guys are Ninjas known for
continuing to fight

239
00:16:01,609 --> 00:16:03,702
no matter what the sacrifice.

240
00:16:05,346 --> 00:16:07,644
How were you able
to detect our movements?

241
00:16:08,883 --> 00:16:10,908
There probably wouldn't be
puddles of water

242
00:16:11,486 --> 00:16:15,445
on a clear day like today,
when it hasn't rained for days.

243
00:16:16,591 --> 00:16:20,118
Knowing that, why'd you leave it
to the kids to fight?

244
00:16:21,062 --> 00:16:24,964
If I felt like it,
I could kill these guys instantly...

245
00:16:25,767 --> 00:16:29,999
But...
I had to know...

246
00:16:31,539 --> 00:16:34,804
who the target
of these enemies was...

247
00:16:35,376 --> 00:16:37,742
Hm?! What do you mean?

248
00:16:38,846 --> 00:16:39,642
In other words...

249
00:16:39,881 --> 00:16:42,577
what I mean is I had to know
if it was you,

250
00:16:43,251 --> 00:16:48,746
or one of us Shinobi...
who was being targeted.

251
00:16:50,058 --> 00:16:54,586
We haven't heard anything about
you being targeted by Ninjas.

252
00:16:55,563 --> 00:16:58,555
The content of the request was
supposed to just be

253
00:16:58,633 --> 00:17:01,625
protection from gangs,
thieves, and the like...

254
00:17:02,570 --> 00:17:05,596
This is a mission with
a B rank or higher.

255
00:17:07,175 --> 00:17:08,301
The request was supposed to be

256
00:17:08,376 --> 00:17:11,368
for backup protection
until you finished building your bridge...

257
00:17:13,347 --> 00:17:15,315
If our enemies were to be Ninjas,

258
00:17:15,383 --> 00:17:17,442
the mission would've been
estimated without question

259
00:17:17,518 --> 00:17:19,452
as an expensive
"B Rank" mission.

260
00:17:20,922 --> 00:17:22,890
It appears there's some kind
of good reason for this,

261
00:17:23,424 --> 00:17:25,915
but being lied to in the request
won't do.

262
00:17:26,427 --> 00:17:30,193
This is beyond the scope
of our mission.

263
00:17:31,365 --> 00:17:34,198
This mission is too soon for us...

264
00:17:34,969 --> 00:17:35,958
Let's give it up!

265
00:17:37,171 --> 00:17:39,139
We need an anesthetic to
open Naruto's wound

266
00:17:39,207 --> 00:17:41,471
and get out the poisoned blood...

267
00:17:42,210 --> 00:17:44,440
We have to return to the village
and take him to a doctor...

268
00:17:45,480 --> 00:17:46,504
Hmmm...

269
00:17:48,916 --> 00:17:49,883
Hm? What?!

270
00:17:52,887 --> 00:17:54,582
This sure is a burden!

271
00:17:55,089 --> 00:17:58,354
Since we need to treat Naruto's wound,
shall we go back to the village...?

272
00:18:07,301 --> 00:18:07,733
Huh!

273
00:18:07,935 --> 00:18:08,333
Oh!

274
00:18:16,377 --> 00:18:18,174
<i>Why am I so different?!</i>

275
00:18:18,679 --> 00:18:22,581
<i>Why's it always me...</i>
<i>Damn it!</i>

276
00:18:22,650 --> 00:18:25,175
Naruto! What're you doing?!

277
00:18:26,988 --> 00:18:29,718
<i>I should be getting stronger...</i>

278
00:18:30,558 --> 00:18:32,423
<i>Here I'm steadily carrying</i>
<i>out missions and</i>

279
00:18:32,493 --> 00:18:35,155
<i>doing special skill training</i>
<i>by myself every day...</i>

280
00:18:38,966 --> 00:18:43,403
<i>I'll never get into another situation</i>
<i>from which I'll have to be rescued.</i>

281
00:18:44,972 --> 00:18:47,736
<i>I'll never be afraid</i>
<i>or a be a coward...</i>

282
00:18:49,110 --> 00:18:51,101
<i>I won't lose to Sasuke...</i>

283
00:18:53,147 --> 00:18:56,480
I'm going to swear on
the pain of my left hand!

284
00:18:58,786 --> 00:19:02,017
I'll protect you, old man...
with this Kunai knife!!

285
00:19:09,197 --> 00:19:10,858
The mission continues!!

286
00:19:11,632 --> 00:19:12,496
Naruto...

287
00:19:12,967 --> 00:19:15,731
It's all well and good to
rid yourself of the poisoned blood,

288
00:19:15,803 --> 00:19:18,465
but any more than that and
you'll bleed to death.

289
00:19:28,115 --> 00:19:30,743
Things will get hairy if you don't
stop the bleeding quick... Seriously!

290
00:19:30,918 --> 00:19:31,475
Yikes!

291
00:19:32,220 --> 00:19:34,620
Argh! No! No!

292
00:19:34,689 --> 00:19:36,987
I can't die like this, I say!

293
00:19:37,191 --> 00:19:38,783
Show me your hand.

294
00:19:38,893 --> 00:19:41,361
Nooo! Help me!!

295
00:19:41,429 --> 00:19:42,396
Naruto!

296
00:19:42,730 --> 00:19:44,960
You're really self abusive,
aren't you!

297
00:19:45,666 --> 00:19:46,963
That's masochistic!

298
00:19:54,041 --> 00:19:55,269
<i>The wound is...</i>

299
00:19:56,244 --> 00:19:57,302
<i>already starting to heal...</i>

300
00:20:01,849 --> 00:20:03,146
Um... um...

301
00:20:04,285 --> 00:20:08,745
Am I okay?
You look awfully serious...

302
00:20:10,124 --> 00:20:11,921
Well... You should be okay.

303
00:20:13,861 --> 00:20:16,557
<i>Is it...the power of</i>
<i>the Nine Tailed Fox...?</i>

304
00:20:25,640 --> 00:20:27,540
Did you say you failed?!

305
00:20:28,242 --> 00:20:31,439
I paid a lot of money to hire
you guys

306
00:20:31,512 --> 00:20:34,276
because you said
you were once hot shot Ninjas!

307
00:20:35,316 --> 00:20:37,807
Stop your damned grumbling...!!

308
00:20:41,622 --> 00:20:48,221
Next time, I'll kill him with this...
head chopper!

309
00:20:50,464 --> 00:20:52,830
I-It's really okay, right?!

310
00:20:53,534 --> 00:20:56,731
It seems that the enemy
has hired good Ninjas...

311
00:20:56,871 --> 00:21:01,467
On top of that, a tightened guard
on account of the Demon Brothers' failure

312
00:21:01,542 --> 00:21:03,339
means that it won't be easy...

313
00:21:03,411 --> 00:21:06,244
Just who do you think I am?!

314
00:21:10,518 --> 00:21:14,010
This Zabuza Momochi,
who is called the demon of...

315
00:21:14,455 --> 00:21:16,480
the Hidden Mist!!

316
00:22:52,395 --> 00:22:54,625
We've finally landed ashore
in the Land of the Waves.

317
00:22:54,864 --> 00:22:56,058
The guys before were
all well and good,

318
00:22:56,132 --> 00:22:58,566
but there should be even
stronger guys lying in wait.

319
00:22:58,834 --> 00:23:01,632
Okay! I'm going to regain
my honor and continue the mission.

320
00:23:01,804 --> 00:23:03,203
No matter what enemy comes,

321
00:23:03,272 --> 00:23:05,399
I'll protect the old man
this time around for sure.

322
00:23:05,474 --> 00:23:07,704
Oh, they wasted no time.

323
00:23:07,943 --> 00:23:10,605
An impressive looking guy with
a huge Katana has come.

324
00:23:11,580 --> 00:23:13,275
Next episode:
"The Assassin of the Mist!"

325
00:23:13,549 --> 00:23:16,347
I'm going to kick butt once again!
